<lb n="0670b22" ed="T"/>藐訖三<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">十</note>　怛儞也<note place="inline">二合引</note>他<note place="inline">去引</note><note place="inline">十一</note>　素嚕
